{"word":"Barnabas","slug":"barnabas","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Barnabas</b> <a href=\"#/G921\">G921</a> <br/> Called also Joses.<br/> A prophet<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=13&verse=1'>Act 13:1</a><br/> An apostle<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=14&verse=14'>Act 14:14</a><br/> A Levite who gave his possessions to be owned in common with other disciples<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=4&verse=37'>Act 4:37</a><br/> Goes to Antioch to find Paul, brings him to Antioch<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=9&verse=27'>Act 9:27</a><br/> Accompanies Paul to Jerusalem<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=11&verse=30'>Act 11:30</a><br/> Returns with Paul to Antioch<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=12&verse=25'>Act 12:25</a><br/> Goes with Paul to Seleucia<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=13'>Act 13</a><br/> Goes with Paul to Iconium<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=14&verse=7'>Act 14:7</a><br/> Called Jupiter<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=14&verse=18'>Act 14:18</a><br/> Goes to Derbe<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=14&verse=20'>Act 14:20</a><br/> Is sent as a commissioner to Jerusalem<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=15'>Act 15</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=48&chapter=2&verse=9'>Gal 2:9</a><br/> Disaffected towards Paul<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=15&verse=39'>Act 15:39</a><br/> Is reconciled to Paul<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=46&chapter=9&verse=6'>1Co 9:6</a><br/> Piety of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=11&verse=24'>Act 11:24</a><br/> Devotion of, to Jesus<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=15&verse=26'>Act 15:26</a>"}]}